Your `@EmbeddedId` seems to be complicating the matters and confusing you, without serving any useful purpose that I can discern, so I recommend getting rid of it.  That would leave you with:
```
@Entity
@NoArgsConstructor
@AllArgsConstructor
@Getter
@Setter
@ToString
public class PersonRace {
    @Id
    @NotNull
    @ManyToOne
    @Column(name = &quot;race_id&quot;)
    private Race race;

    @Id
    @NotNull
    @ManyToOne
    @Column(name = &quot;person_id&quot;)
