**Second**, Machine sends following query at first time:

    1H|\^&amp;|||CS-2500^^22029^^^CP^BV981798||||||||E1394-9711
    2Q|1|000038^01^   0012365845B||^^^040^PT-INN\^^^050^APTT-FS|0|201803081227007F
